::Havotron/Dreadwind/Darkwing::
Havotron walked into the meeting as Reflector left.
"Anoying bots those three are...." he commented. He then turned to the 
small council of dark leaders.
"Commander Havotron reporting.  What are our plans?"
Dreadwind walked behind him and kneeled towards the council.
"What is the point of this. Fighting does nothing."

Darkwing also came and kneeled.
"Finally we shall fight. I just wish my brother would be left here the 
whiner that he is."
